data.title: Suleiman the Magnificent Osman ibn Selim, Sultan of the Ottoman Empire, b.1494 d.1566
data.meta_description: Suleiman the Magnificent Osman ibn Selim, Sultan of the Ottoman Empire born 1494 in Trabzon, Trabzon, Turkey genealogy record - Ancestry®.
data.text:
Born in Trabzon, Trabzon, Turkey on 6 November 1494 to Selim I, Sultan of the Ottoman Empire and Ayşe Hafsa Sultan (Giray) de Khanids. Suleiman the Magnificent Osman ibn Selim, Sultan of the Ottoman Empire married Хюррем кадън Лисовска and had 7 children. He passed away on 6 September 1566 in Szigetvár, Baranya, Hungary.
